text: Everything that has a beginning has an end.
We can never see past the choices we don’t understand.
Nothing ever works out just the way you want it to.
We’re all here to do what we’re all here to do.
You'll remember you don't believe in any of this fate crap. You're in control of your own life, remember?
Sorry, kid. You got the gift, but it looks like you're waiting for something.
You didn't come here to make the choice. you've already made it. You're here to try to understand why you made it.
